short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Codingame with your own overlays in visualizer.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
On Codingame.com IDE and replay page parses your bot stderr output and interpret it as instructions to draw overlays on CG game visualizer.

See https://github.com/xoposhiy/cg-overlays for details
